name: v1.7.1
body:
- Changed default API
- Changed logo and profile images

name: v1.7
body: Added the ability to select the date to view the schedule. The settings now have a choice between displaying numbers and days of the week.

name: v1.6
body:
Redesigned the design of the application and the widget - now the names of items will be placed in small screens🎉
Fixed a bunch of bugs

name: v1.5
body:
Redesigned the system of abbreviated item titles and added the ability to disable this feature. Now you can choose any of the three APIs in the settings. This will help you in case of failures on the official website of RANEPA services. 
Fixed a bug with a white dial when selecting a dark theme for an alarm clock. 
Redesigned start screen and About section. 
Fixed minor bugs.

name: v1.4
body:
Now you can choose between displaying text and icons to indicate the body of the lesson
The theme system has been reworked - now you can select the theme style and color separately
Some bugs fixed
Now, if there is any error in the application, instead of the red screen, the offer to send information about the error to the developers will be displayed

name: v1.3
body:
Optimized initial setup
Fixed a few bugs
The application is fully migrated to the same API that is used on the official website.
Slightly changed widget

name: v1.2.1
body:
Replaced application icon
Added schedule update button

name: v1.2
body:
Added some lesson icons.
Application migrated to new API
Removed attributes of RANEPA at the request of the administration

name: v1.1
body:
Reworked widget
Changed the screen "About"
Fixed minor bugs

name: v1.0.1
body:
Fixed problems with the long title of academic disciplines
Minor bugs fixed
